Internal handling of values
---------------------------

## Supported types
  Nil             0
  Integer         1
  Float           2
  String          3
  Array           4
  Table           5
  Function        6
  NativePointer   7

## Supertables
  Non-function values: copied
  Function values: reference

## Operator overloading
  sum   +
  sub   -
  mul   *
  div   /
  idiv  |/
  mod   %
  eq    ==  (automatic: neq)
  lt    <   (automatic: lte)
  gt    >   (automatic: gte)
  and   &
  or    |
  xor   ~
  pow   ^
  shl   <<
  shr   >>

## Error format

{ error: "Error message" }

Additional fields:
  if debugging info: file + line
  if no debugging info: function_id + pc

Errors:
  - OutOfRange
